:* {{ill|Amaterasu|ja|天照大神|1=Amaterasu|lt=Amaterasu Ōmikami|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Amaterasu|13=User:Immanuelle/Amaterasu|qq=}}
:* {{ill|Tatemizukata no Kami|ja|建水方神|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tatemizukata no Kami|qq=}} (believed to be the same as {{ill|Tatemikata no Kami|ja|建御名方神|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tatemikata no Kami|qq=}})
; Co-Enshrined
:* {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|菅原道真|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sugawara no Michizane|qq=}}

== Transportation ==
* Get off at the "Ono" bus stop of the {{ill|Meitetsu Bus|ja|名鉄バス|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meitetsu Bus|qq=}} and walk for 3 minutes.
