** From {{ill|Meitetsu|ja|名鉄|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meitetsu|1=Q11415661|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11415661}}’s {{ill|Meitetsu Nagoya Main Line|en|Meitetsu Nagoya Main Line|WD=Q1137838|lt=Nagoya Main Line|1=Meitetsu Nagoya Main Line}} and {{ill|Meitetsu Bisai Line|en|Meitetsu Bisai Line|WD=Q901005|lt=Meitetsu Onishi Line|1=Meitetsu Bisai Line}} at {{ill|Meitetsu Ichinomiya Station|en|Meitetsu Ichinomiya Station|WD=Q2856589|lt=Meitetsu Ichinomiya Station|1=Meitetsu Ichinomiya Station}}, or from the {{ill|Tōkaidō Main Line|ja|Tōkaidō Main Line|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tōkaidō Main Line|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} at {{ill|Owari-Ichinomiya Station|en|Owari-Ichinomiya Station|WD=Q871495|lt=Owari Ichinomiya Station|1=Owari-Ichinomiya Station}} (Platform 3 at the {{ill|Meitetsu Ichinomiya Station Bus Terminal|ja|名鉄一宮駅バスターミナル|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meitetsu Ichinomiya Station Bus Terminal|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 一宮駅バスターミナル|1=Q11415757|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11415757}}) for the "Kawashima" bus.

